            <answer>A</answer><explanation>Shifted sine/cosine intersection at pi/8.</explanation></question>
        <question>
            <text>Area of region bounded by x^2/16 + y^2/9 = 1 and line x/4 + y/3 = 1 (smaller part):</text>
            <option id="A">3(pi - 2)</option><option id="B">12(pi - 1)</option><option id="C">None</option><option id="D">D</option>
