            <answer>D</answer><explanation>Integral 1 to 9 x^{1/2} dx = 2/3(27 - 1) = 52/3 approx 17.33.</explanation></question>
        <question>
            <text>Area bounded by y^2 = x and line x + y = 2:</text>
            <option id="A">4.5</option><option id="B">9</option><option id="C">None</option><option id="D">D</option>
            <answer>A</answer><explanation>Intersection at y = 1, -2. Integral -2 to 1 (2-y - y^2) dy = 4.5.</explanation></question>
        <question>
            <text>Are under y = sin x from x=0 to x=pi is S. Area under y = sin^2 x is:</text>
